 operation in the first region of the touch control screen; detecting to obtain a working mode of the touch control screen when there is the first touch control operation; generating a first control instruction based on the first touch control operation when the working mode is a first extended working mode, the second display screen corresponding to the the first extended working mode in at least one display screen being capable to obtain and display a first execution result.</p></abstract></us-patent-application>